   "fetchAvailableTags uses .checkbox-group.genres .checkbox-wrapper instead of div.genres .checkbox.",
   "The selectors/capabilities above are recorded for reference; the base MadthemeEngine pipeline (div.book-item list + bookSlug chapter API) will NOT parse this source correctly. Needs a bespoke engine or an escape-hatch flow."
